<br>
Okay, several years ago, my mother picked up two books in this four book series at a Christian book fair.  It's a sci-fi series about a girl's journey to God -in a surreal universe- and her romance with a boy she meets there.  I thought it was pretty good, but when I went to purchase the last book -to find out how it ends b/c it drives me nuts not knowing- I discovered that the series wasn't in circulation anymore!<br>
<br>
The author, Thomas Locke, only wrote six books with Bethany House Publishers, and of those six, none are published anymore.  In fact, he isn't even listed as a Bethany author on Bethany House's website!<br>
<br>
I was wondering if anyone had ever heard of the series, read the books, or knew where I could find them -short of Amazon.com (the only place I could find them! and that was in the used book section!).<br>
